# Required technologies

1. Python
2. ReportLab - library to work with PDFs (allows to create tables)
3. Flask (to create basic UI)


# Information to include on the Invoice

1. About me:
    [company name]
    [street address]
    [city, zip]
    [phone number]
    [website/contact media/email]

2. Bill to:
    [name of contractor]
    [company name]
    [street address]
    [city, zip]
    [phone number]

3. Easily noticeable captions "INVOICE"

4. # of invoice issued

5. Invoice issue date

6. Full service description with corresponding KVEDs

7. Amount of the payment

8. Total $

9. Service conduction date interval